'''朱頌霏'''<ref name="bbczw" />（{{lang-en|Hazel Chu}}，{{bd|1980年|||}}）<ref name="Indo_2020_prfl">{{cite news |last1=McCarthy |first1=Mary |title=This Working Life: The stress of politics? I'm thinking of taking up boxing gloves next |url=https://www.independent.ie/business/irish/this-working-life-the-stress-of-politics-im-thinking-of-taking-up-boxing-gloves-next-39371278.html |access-date=2021-01-23 |work=爱尔兰独立报 |date=2020-07-16 |language=en |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204120822/https://www.independent.ie/business/irish/this-working-life-the-stress-of-politics-im-thinking-of-taking-up-boxing-gloves-next-39371278.html |dead-url=no }}{{paywall}}</ref>，[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]女政治家，首都[[都柏林|都柏林]]市市长（2020年6月－2021年6月）、[[綠黨_(愛爾蘭)|綠黨]]黨主席。朱頌霏也是爱尔兰共和国历史上首位华裔市长。

== 家庭背景 ==
朱頌霏的父母为[[英屬香港|英屬香港]][[新界原居民|新界原居民]]，<ref name="bbczw">{{cite web |author1=BBC中文网 |title=朱頌霏：愛爾蘭都柏林首位華裔市長 父母是香港新界原居民 |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEBOo4UiIWQ |website=YouTube |accessdate=2021-01-31 |archive-date=2021-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210623030754/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEBOo4UiIWQ |dead-url=no }}</ref>父亲来自[[沙頭角|沙頭角]][[鹿頸|鹿頸]]附近的雞谷樹下，母亲来自[[沙田_(香港)|沙田]][[小瀝源|小瀝源]]<ref name="billy" />，两人在[[1970年代香港|1970年代]]的[[香港移民潮|香港移民潮]]中移居爱尔兰。<ref name="SCMP_prof">{{cite news |last1=Carney |first1=John |title=Dublin’s first ethnic-Chinese mayor on racism, her parents’ work ethic, and teaching poor children in China |url=https://www.scmp.com/lifestyle/article/3095902/dublins-first-ethnic-chinese-mayor-racism-her-parents-work-ethic-and |access-date=2021-01-23 |work=[[南华早报|南华早报]] |date=2020-08-05 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311001907/https://www.scmp.com/lifestyle/article/3095902/dublins-first-ethnic-chinese-mayor-racism-her-parents-work-ethic-and |dead-url=no }}</ref>移居至爱尔兰后，父亲曾于餐厅工作，并和朱頌霏的母亲相遇，两人曾经经营过流动小吃摊贩和中餐馆。朱頌霏的父母离异后，父亲回到香港经营咖啡馆，而母亲则继续留在爱尔兰经营多间中餐馆，朱頌霏也不时来往香港和爱尔兰两地探望家人。

朱頌霏于1980年11月在都柏林出生，早年就读于[[都柏林大学_(爱尔兰国立大学)|爱尔兰国立大学都柏林分校]]，并参与校内的辩论队，后来于{{link-en|国王因斯学会|King's Inns}}就读法学，成为爱尔兰首位獲授予出庭資格的华裔律师<ref name="UCD">{{cite web |url=https://www.ucd.ie/businessalumni/news/inprofile/hazelchumsc11/ |title=Hazel Chu |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=2019-03 |website=ucd.ie |access-date=2020-01-12 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109010807/https://www.ucd.ie/businessalumni/news/inprofile/hazelchumsc11/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Edu_IT_2019">{{cite news |last1=McMahon |first1=Áine |title=My education journey: Hazel Chu – Dublin City councillor and Green Party co-ordinator |url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/education/my-education-journey-hazel-chu-dublin-city-councillor-and-green-party-co-ordinator-1.3979573 |access-date=2020-01-12 |work=[[爱尔兰时报|爱尔兰时报]] |date=2019-08-13 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107232758/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/education/my-education-journey-hazel-chu-dublin-city-councillor-and-green-party-co-ordinator-1.3979573 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。毕业后，朱頌霏曾在中国[[广西壮族自治区|广西壮族自治区]]的偏远地区学校担任志愿教师<ref name="SCMP_prof" />，也曾于爱尔兰国内、澳大利亚、新西兰和美国多地工作<ref name="Indo_2020_prfl" />，受聘于[[帝亞吉歐|帝亞吉歐]]等企业和机构。朱頌霏现和愛爾蘭綠黨黨员{{link-en|帕特里克·科斯特洛|Patrick Costello (politician)}}育有一女。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.image.ie/life/women-in-politics-hazel-chu-could-be-the-first-ever-irish-born-chinese-politician-to-be-elected-in-the-irish-state-136959 |title=Women in politics: Hazel Chu could be the first ever Irish Born Chinese politician to be elected in the Irish State |last=O'Donoghue |first=Niamh |date=2018-12-22 |website=image.ie |access-date=2020-01-12 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129141242/https://www.image.ie/life/women-in-politics-hazel-chu-could-be-the-first-ever-irish-born-chinese-politician-to-be-elected-in-the-irish-state-136959 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 政治生涯 ==
2014年，朱頌霏开始为愛爾蘭綠黨成员帕特里克·科斯特洛助选都柏林市议员，两年后加入綠黨，并于2019年12月当选该党党主席<ref name="Cathaoirleach ">{{cite news |last=Quann |first=Jack |date=2019-11-29 |title=Hazel Chu elected Cathaoirleach of The Green Party |url=https://www.newstalk.com/news/hazel-chu-elected-cathaoirleach-green-party-931024 |work=newstalk |access-date=2020-01-12 |language=en |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204223312/https://www.newstalk.com/news/hazel-chu-elected-cathaoirleach-green-party-931024 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年6月29日，朱頌霏当选第352任都柏林市市长，任期为一年。朱頌霏成为爱尔兰共和国首位[[有色人种|有色人种]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Moore |first=Aoife |date=2021-01-22 |title=Lord mayor of Dublin harassed at her home by far-right protestors |url=https://www.irishexaminer.com/news/politics/arid-40211837.html |work=Irish Examiner |access-date=2021-01-24 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322040442/https://www.irishexaminer.com/news/politics/arid-40211837.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、首位华裔市长，也是担任欧洲各国首都市长的首位华裔女性。<ref name="lhb">{{cite news|author=徐榆涵|url=https://udn.com/news/story/120883/4761251|title=都柏林首位華裔女市長仍飽受歧視之苦 她被嗆滾回中國|date=2020-08-07|work=聯合報|language=zh-tw|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926002804/https://udn.com/news/story/120883/4761251|dead-url=no}}{{paywall}}</ref><ref name="billy">{{cite news |first=Billy |last=Tong |url=https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/09/16/hazel-chu/ |title=港人後代：都柏林的朱市長 |work=[[茶杯雜誌|茶杯雜誌]] |language=zh-hk |accessdate=2021-01-31 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204230218/https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/09/16/hazel-chu/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在担任市长和竞选都柏林市议员期间，朱頌霏受到了种族歧视<ref name="bbczw" /><ref name="lhb" />和质疑她的华裔背景<ref>{{cite news |last=O'Connor |first=Rachel |date=2019-09-30 |title=Irish far-right National Party leader doused with milkshake during event in Galway |url=https://www.irishpost.com/news/irish-far-right-national-party-politician-doused-milkshake-speech-galway-171897 |work=Irish Post |access-date=2020-01-12 |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108084128/https://www.irishpost.com/news/irish-far-right-national-party-politician-doused-milkshake-speech-galway-171897 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="This is happening">{{cite news |last=O’Donoghue |first=Denise |date=2019-08-12 |title='This is happening in our own country': Dublin councillor Hazel Chu hits out at racist abuse and Nazi salutes |url=https://www.breakingnews.ie/ireland/this-is-happening-in-our-own-country-dublin-councillor-hazel-chu-hits-out-at-racist-abuse-and-nazi-salutes-943360.html |work=BreakingNews.ie |access-date=2020-01-12 |language=en |archive-date=2020-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200112023825/https://www.breakingnews.ie/ireland/this-is-happening-in-our-own-country-dublin-councillor-hazel-chu-hits-out-at-racist-abuse-and-nazi-salutes-943360.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也有极右翼示威者在[[市长官邸_(都柏林)|都柏林市长官邸]]前示威，向她和女儿辱骂<ref>{{cite news |title=Chu 'fears for daughter's safety' amid racist abuse |url=https://www.rte.ie/news/ireland/2021/0122/1191430-hazel-chu/ |accessdate=2021-01-31 |work=[[爱尔兰广播电视|爱尔兰广播电视]] |date=2021-01-22 |language=en |archive-date=2021-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201073745/https://www.rte.ie/news/ireland/2021/0122/1191430-hazel-chu/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

朱頌霏也关心[[香港|香港]]的政制发展，在Twitter评论[[2019年香港區議會選舉|2019年香港區議會選舉]]时表示为香港人加油<ref>{{cite twitter|user=hazechu |number=1198718014461534209 |date=2019-11-24 |title=Hong Kong voters turn out in force to give the government a spanking! 71% whooping turnout, many who have never voted before. Gwan [go on] #HongKongers!}}</ref>。

